OOC: There was no actual blood, only energon and energy that would 
cause damages since the concentration was so high.

BIC:

Tyrael was up in the air when he saw the incoming Proto.

Tyrael: I don't know how you survived, but I'll correct the situation 
myself!

He sent a wide beam of burning light at the hawk-shaped bot.

Down on the ground, Vlad was having an equally challenging combat. He 
loved that. His new body did not give the usual edge he had, but his 
reinforced armor gave him confidence.

He turned to receive a blast in the left side, then rolled to 
Wolfenstein and let go of two punches and a missile volley at 
point-blank range.
